</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Sorry if I implied you alone. You'll see that I said "They say," as in Covetous Crew. You were vigorously defending your friends because DOT was "The only way they could defend themselves." ( Against a character who couldn't damage them more than a bar to begin with ). And as soon as the GM left, you were all shouting "Have fun losing experience." "There goes another bar of experience." You are OBVIOUSLY exploiting on purpose, whether it was you personally or just you encouraging and defending your guildmates. Either way, you were exploiting a bug to harm another player, period, end of story.

